The package jgd-cmake-modules provides CMake modules:

    find_package(jgd-cmake-modules REQUIRED CONFIG)
    include(JcmAllModules)   # include all modules
    include(JcmSetupProject) # OR include specific modules
    jcm_setup_project()      # use modules

For more information, see https://github.com/jgd-solutions/jgd-cmake-modules
